             was indicted for <rs id="t18330905-171-off946" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18330905-171-off946" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18330905-171-off946" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18330905-171-cd947" type="crimeDate">17th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18330905-171-off946 t18330905-171-cd947"></join>, 10 yards of velvet, value 3l.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18330905-171-victim1634" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Rozee
                  <interp inst="t18330905-171-victim1634" type="surname" value="Rozee"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18330905-171-victim1634" type="given" value="James"></interp>
